# Services

## Frontend Services
- [frontend/src/services/AuthService.ts](mdc:frontend/src/services/AuthService.ts) - Authentication service for login/logout
- [frontend/src/services/UserService.ts](mdc:frontend/src/services/UserService.ts) - User management service

## Backend Services
- [backend/app/services/auth_service.py](mdc:backend/app/services/auth_service.py) - Backend authentication service
- [backend/app/services/user_service.py](mdc:backend/app/services/user_service.py) - Backend user management service

## API Endpoints
- `/auth/login` - User authentication
- `/auth/me` - Get current user info
- `/users` - User management endpoints
  - GET - List users
  - POST - Create user
  - PUT - Update user
  - DELETE - Delete user

